name: Bella Hadid
description:
Bella Hadid

Supermodel

Continuing testing my LoRA prowess, here is world famous model Bella Hadid. I know next to nothing about her other than she was the subject of a LoRA once, by me.

I used 30 high-definition images, 75 steps each, kohya_ss defaults otherwise.

Do you like my work? Buy me a beer!

She looks best 0.6-0.8, gradients included in my examples below.
